text: Kacheganovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kacheganovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 558 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Kacheganovo
